
SYSADMIN:::

system monitoring software(app) on python:

1]
show the Load Averages, for last 1, 5, 10 mins 
with good visuals on Raphael or other JS charts
command: top (take load averages)

2]
show processes and theirs names,
with different colors.
command: ps -ef

3]
change Unix pass for a System User
[shadow file]

4]
show hard disk health

5]
networking functionalities
>
chk/change system ip
>
up/down interface
#ifup/ifdown <interface>
show progress, up or down


